WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:06.560
[BELLS RINGING]
&gt;&gt;[SOUNDS OF ALARM] WHAT MATTER OF

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:07.560
MADNESS ARE YOU?

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:09.870
&gt;&gt;I AM THE GHOST OF CHRISTMAS PAST.

00:00:09.870 --> 00:00:13.150
THE FIRST OF THREE SPIRITS, WHICH WILL VISIT
YOU THIS NIGHT.

00:00:13.150 --> 00:00:15.529
&gt;&gt;WHY WOULD YOU COME TO TORTURE A POOR OLD
MAN?

00:00:15.529 --> 00:00:20.110
&gt;&gt;BECAUSE IF YOU DO NOT CHANGE YOUR WAYS
THY SOUL WILL BE TAKEN.

00:00:20.110 --> 00:00:26.510
&gt;&gt;WHO YOU GOING TO CALL?

00:00:26.510 --> 00:00:30.350
&gt;&gt;WHO ARE YOU?

00:00:30.350 --> 00:00:33.410
&gt;&gt;I’M YOUR WORST NIGHTMARE GHOST.

00:00:33.410 --> 00:00:35.400
&gt;&gt;WHERE’S THE GHOST OF CHRISTMAS PRESENT?

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:37.899
&gt;&gt;YOU MEAN GHOST OF CHRISTMAS PAST?

00:00:37.899 --> 00:00:38.899
&gt;&gt;NO.

00:00:38.899 --> 00:00:40.990
I’M THE GHOST OF CHRISTMAS PAST.

00:00:40.990 --> 00:00:43.710
&gt;&gt;WELL SO IS HE BECAUSE I TRAPPED HIM SO HE’S
NO

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:44.710
LONGER IN THE PRESENT.

00:00:44.710 --> 00:00:45.710
HE’S IN THE-- HE’S IN THE PAST.

00:00:45.710 --> 00:00:46.800
&gt;&gt;WE GET IT YOU FOOL.

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:49.899
SCROOGE NEEDED TO HEAR HIS MESSAGE.

00:00:49.899 --> 00:00:54.550
&gt;&gt;WHAT’S GOING ON HERE?

00:00:54.550 --> 00:00:58.020
&gt;&gt;GHOST!

00:00:58.020 --> 00:01:03.910
&gt;&gt;YOU JUST VAPORIZED MY OLD PARTNER!

00:01:03.910 --> 00:01:05.720
GOOD SHOW!

00:01:05.720 --> 00:01:07.530
&gt;&gt;BOO YAH!

00:01:07.530 --> 00:01:10.310
OR SHOULD I SAY BOO NAH BECAUSE HE’S GONE!

00:01:10.310 --> 00:01:11.460
[LAUGHTER] GHOST PUN!

00:01:11.460 --> 00:01:12.460
YEAH!

00:01:12.460 --> 00:01:13.460
&gt;&gt;NO MORE!

00:01:13.460 --> 00:01:16.510
DON’T YOU DARE SHOOT CHRISTMAS FUTURE!

00:01:16.510 --> 00:01:18.060
NO!

00:01:18.060 --> 00:01:19.619
&gt;&gt;GHOST!

00:01:19.619 --> 00:01:24.280
&gt;&gt;WHAT WAS THAT?

00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:26.210
&gt;&gt;THAT WAS SELF-DEFENSE.

00:01:26.210 --> 00:01:28.470
&gt;&gt;SELF DEFENSE?

00:01:28.470 --> 00:01:30.259
WHO ALL ELSE IS IN HERE?

00:01:30.259 --> 00:01:37.719
&gt;&gt;LET’S SEE THERE’S THE HOGWARTS GHOST,
THE GHOST OF ELVIS, AND THE PAC-MAN GHOST.

00:01:37.719 --> 00:01:44.869
[PAC-MAN MUSIC] [KNOCK ON THE DOOR]
&gt;&gt;MR.

00:01:44.869 --> 00:01:46.900
SCROOGE SIR.

00:01:46.900 --> 00:01:54.020
COULD YOU SPARE A FARTHING FOR--
&gt;&gt;GHOST!

00:01:54.020 --> 00:01:56.229
[SCREAMING] THAT WAS ALSO SELF-DEFENSE.

00:01:56.229 --> 00:02:00.579
&gt;&gt;THAT WAS TINY TIM!

00:02:00.579 --> 00:02:04.170
&gt;&gt;YES, BUT HE TOTALLY DODGED MY PROTON STREAM
SO.

00:02:04.170 --> 00:02:05.170
&gt;&gt;OH REALLY?

00:02:05.170 --> 00:02:06.170
&gt;&gt;YEP!

00:02:06.170 --> 00:02:07.170
HE’S SURPRISINGLY AGILE.

00:02:07.170 --> 00:02:08.170
&gt;&gt;HELLO?

00:02:08.170 --> 00:02:09.170
CAN ANYONE HEAR ME?

00:02:09.170 --> 00:02:10.770
&gt;&gt;IS THAT TINY TIM?

00:02:10.770 --> 00:02:11.770
&gt;&gt;NO!

00:02:11.770 --> 00:02:13.849
NO, THAT’S PETITE PAUL.

00:02:13.849 --> 00:02:16.459
&gt;&gt;YOU’RE A MONSTER!

00:02:16.459 --> 00:02:21.280
&gt;&gt;LOOK GUYS, TIM PROBABLY GOT
WHAT HE DESERVED.

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:23.860
&gt;&gt;GOD BLESS US EVERYONE!

00:02:23.860 --> 00:02:27.890
EVEN THE MAN THAT PUT ME IN HERE.

00:02:27.890 --> 00:02:28.890
&gt;&gt;YOU KNOW MR.

00:02:28.890 --> 00:02:30.910
SCROOGE, IN COMPARISON YOU HAVING
PEOPLE WORK ON CHRISTMAS DOESN’T SEEM SO

00:02:30.910 --> 00:02:31.910
BAD ANYMORE.

00:02:31.910 --> 00:02:32.910
&gt;&gt;BAH HUMBUG!

00:02:32.910 --> 00:02:36.420
&gt;&gt;LOOK GUYS, I’VE MADE SOME MISTAKES,
BUT IT’S CHRISTMAS!

00:02:36.420 --> 00:02:37.850
WHAT WOULD TIM WANT?

00:02:37.850 --> 00:02:39.740
&gt;&gt;PEACE ON EARTH!

00:02:39.740 --> 00:02:41.569
&gt;&gt;SHUT UP TIM!

00:02:41.569 --> 00:02:45.610
&gt;&gt;FINE, WE WILL FORGIVE YOU THIS ONCE,
BUT DON’T LET ANYTHING LIKE THIS HAPPEN

00:02:45.610 --> 00:02:46.610
EVER AGAIN.

00:02:46.610 --> 00:02:47.930
&gt;&gt;I WON’T.
THANK YOU GUYS!

00:02:47.930 --> 00:02:48.930
&gt;&gt;HI!

00:02:48.930 --> 00:02:54.080
SORRY TO BOTHER YOU, BUT DO YOU KNOW WHERE
MY FRIEND CASPER IS?

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:57.609
&gt;&gt;HE REALLY WAS THE FRIENDLIEST.

